description: '''Lincoln Barrett''' (born 18 September 1979), better known by the stage name '''High Contrast''', is a Welsh electronic music producer, [[Disc jockey|DJ]] and [[record producer]]. He produces [[drum and bass]] music, and his 2009 album ''[[Confidential (High Contrast album)|Confidential]]'' reached [[British_Phonographic_Industry|BPI]] gold certification (100,000 units sold in the UK).
